-- Fed: No comment on any AIG job for Morgan Stanley
-- 
-- Mon Sep 15, 2008 1:23pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/15/us-aig-fed-idUSWBT00970120080915

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The New York Federal Reserve declined to comment on Monday on a CNBC report that the Fed has hired Morgan Stanley to negotiate a loan for embattled insurer American International Group Inc. 

 (Reporting by  Mark Felsenthal )